{"tid":1788207,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「王婆婆」自製電子聖誕卡報平安 籲港人「Be Safe」","createTime":"2019-12-18T13:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T13:40:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3a121577c9fd680ae50b059300bb01903a0a6f01","tid":1788207,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:06:10.000Z","msg":"大家集會遊行成日會見到揮英國旗嘅「王婆婆」王鳳瑤，8月於太古警方清場行動中被帶走之後，曾經幾個月時間音訊全無，令唔少港人擔心。臨近聖誕，雖然仲未見到王婆婆露面，但近日有社運界人士就收到佢嘅報平安E-mail，並附上自製電子聖誕卡祝福香港人，十分窩心。<br />\n<br />\n上月臨近區議會選舉，王婆婆曾經以電郵回覆《立場新聞》，提到佢當時喺深圳取保候審，每晚噩夢係重回看守所，而自己一張選票化作廢紙，呼籲港人代為加油，記得要監票留守。<br />\n<br />\n而今次電郵，王婆婆就寫上「I am not bad」報平安，又表示衷心祝福所有香港人，附上一張自製嘅聖誕卡，畫有聖誕樹、笑笑口嘅黃傘，又寫有「民主、人權、自由」等願望，以及「Be Safe」。<br />\n<br />\n對上一次王婆婆公開露面，係8月11日港島東大遊行，夜晚警方清場時，王婆婆喺太古港鐵站C出口外被警員帶離現場，自此缺席所有示威行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191218/60392221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191218%2F60392221&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6pAoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=c342bb68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191218%2F60392221&h=21be561f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191218/60392221</a>"},{"pid":"c34db0fcf5be88031b21651a34a0888e4f0baab0","tid":1788207,"uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191218/large/1576667501_fc92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576667501_fc92.jpg&h=92805dd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"565c3b489d67ba9e968a2234ac8155d3f2b4ce4e","tid":1788207,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:07:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75adaa1ef51e8483067b5f8951146ec8b6e19ce8","ti